68
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:57,110
A teacher for a day is a father for a lifetime.

69
00:04:57,210 --> 00:04:59,130
Master, even if you don't believe me

70
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:00,950
and do nothing about others slandering me,

71
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,660
I hold no grudge against you.

72
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,550
Wu,

73
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:10,750
don't forget

74
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,690
to spit in Third Madam's teacup

75
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,420
and put mud in her rice bowl.

76
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,840
Wu, take this half brick.

77
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:24,680
If you ever run into trouble, just come find me.

78
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:30,730
Senior Brother, don't go!

79
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:37,090
Young Marshal, why are you here?

80
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,300
Just lie down.

81
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:44,930
What's wrong? Thinking about your childhood again?

82
00:05:45,930 --> 00:05:49,940
I dreamt of the fire that burned down my home again.

83
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:53,730
That fire killed my entire family.

84
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:57,220
Before, I could never remember

85
00:05:57,659 --> 00:05:59,370
what happened before the fire.

86
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:03,800
But recently, I suddenly recalled something—

87
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:06,850
my Senior Brother's name was Wu Chongmo.

88
00:06:07,770 --> 00:06:08,720
Are you sure?

89
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,100
My father was his master,

90
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:14,200
but later, he was expelled from the sect by my father.

91
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,190
Could it be that the fire at your home

92
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:20,050
was Wu Chongmo's deliberate act of revenge?

93
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,250
I don't think so.

94
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:29,240
But if he really is the culprit,

95
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,840
I will kill him.

96
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:33,760
Don't worry, we will get to the bottom of this.

97
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:41,890
By the way, any news from Xingrou?

98
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:42,930
Soon.

99
00:06:52,340 --> 00:06:53,159
Qiuting.

100
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:56,909
Dad.

101
00:06:58,330 --> 00:07:00,340
How's the progress on the railway?

102
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,360
It's going smoothly so far.

103
00:07:04,130 --> 00:07:05,190
This time,

104
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:09,760
you must take good care of those foreign experts.

105
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:11,990
Being able to invite them

106
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:13,950
is all thanks to your father-in-law.

107
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:14,980
Also,

108
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:18,880
regarding the railway construction in Jiangxi and Fujian,

109
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:21,700
they've protested to the central government multiple times,

110
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:24,890
and your father-in-law has settled the matter.

111
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:27,120
Got it.

112
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:29,930
I'll personally go to thank him in a few days.

113
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,440
When you go this time,

114
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:35,770
Chief Duan will surely bring up your wedding date.

115
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:38,690
You'd better think carefully—

116
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:41,360
is your romance more important,

117
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:45,210
or is the prosperity of the Yi family?

118
00:07:46,380 --> 00:07:47,110
I understand.

119
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,320
Chengxun.

120
00:07:55,890 --> 00:07:56,730
Xingrou.

121
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:58,180
What are you doing here?

122
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,620
I got your letter saying you're safe.

123
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:00,670
I've been wanting to visit

124
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,770
but didn't want to bother you.

125
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,350
Don't say that, we're friends.

126
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,580
Come home with me, I'll cook for you.

127
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:09,230
Okay.

128
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:11,590
But I can't show up empty-handed.

129
00:08:11,610 --> 00:08:13,070
You go ahead, I'll buy some cake.

130
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:13,720
Alright.

131
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:18,900
Miss Zhao, someone's looking for you.

132
00:08:19,810 --> 00:08:20,330
Coming.

133
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:23,120
Chengxun, why did you get here so fast…

134
00:08:40,990 --> 00:08:41,980
Xingrou,

135
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:45,900
would you really rather stay in this rundown place

136
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:48,070
than come back with me?

137
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,540
Come on, let's go home.

138
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:53,450
Let go of me. I'm not going with you.

139
00:08:55,380 --> 00:08:56,230
Xingrou,

140
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:59,140
I've already given you more than enough freedom.

141
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,540
How much longer are you going to keep this up?

142
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,390
Pack your things.

143
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:05,360
Either you walk out with me,

144
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:07,700
or I carry you out.

145
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:11,160
Yi Qiuting, can't you just let go of me?

146
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:19,400
If you don't want to pack, that's fine.

147
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,560
I'll do it for you.

148
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:27,860
Stop right there!

149
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,450
Yi Qiuting!

150
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:28,930
Let go of me!

151
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,430
Yi Qiuting, what are you doing here?

152
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:31,340
You can't go in!

153
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:35,490
Xingrou, are you alright?

154
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:37,660
Is this really how you've been getting by

155
00:09:37,690 --> 00:09:39,530
this past month?

156
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:41,540
No, it's not what you think.

157
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,190
Is this really how you've been getting by

158
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,800
this past month?

159
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:47,530
Yi Qiuting, you're not allowed to bully Xingrou!

160
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,950
You can get lost now!

161
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:50,180
Chengxun, I...

162
00:09:51,430 --> 00:09:52,480
Xingrou.

163
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:08,790
Yi Qiuting, you're not allowed to bully Xingrou!

164
00:10:08,810 --> 00:10:09,890
Come any closer and I'll shoot.

165
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:18,870
If you keep treating her like this,

166
00:10:18,890 --> 00:10:20,740
how is she supposed to live after this?

167
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:23,320
Get down. Don't move!

168
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,970
Yi Qiuting, you beast!

169
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:40,030
What are you looking at? There's nothing to see here!

170
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,220
Get out of here!

171
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:42,990
Go away!

172
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:04,710
Who is this?

173
00:11:05,770 --> 00:11:07,740
My wife isn't feeling well today,

174
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:10,310
so I'm taking her home.

175
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:11,530
From now on,

176
00:11:11,950 --> 00:11:14,210
she won't be staying here anymore.

177
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,880
This is the Young Marshal's wife.

178
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,570
It's a family matter of the Young Marshal's household.
